第一章
启示

14
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:30,920
吸气 呼气 就像她那样
Breathe in and out, the way she does.

15
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:34,960
现在 用力 快
And now, push. Now!

16
00:02:48,540 --> 00:02:50,070
非常感谢
Thank you so much.

17
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:53,010
再见
Bye.

18
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,940
你过几天再来 对吗
See you in a couple of days, right?

19
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,130
妈妈
Mama...

20
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:14,230
走吗
Are you coming?

21
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:22,670
- 早上好  - 你好 莉兹
- Good morning!  - Hi, Liz!

22
00:03:35,210 --> 00:03:35,920
给
Here.

23
00:04:09,650 --> 00:04:10,960
我不准

24
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,630
莉兹 这孩子得学怎么开枪
Liz, the boy's gotta learn how to shoot.

25
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:13,820
我不允许

26
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,380
他不管怎么样都会学的
Well, he's gonna do it anyway.

27
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:18,090
在这学总好过偷偷在别处学
Better here than sneaking off somewhere else.

28
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:26,100
- 你吓到你母亲了  - 她不是我母亲
- You're scaring your mother.  - She ain't my mother.

29
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:31,070
要防备假先知
Beware of false prophets,

30
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:34,700
他们到你们这里来 外面披着羊皮
who come to you in sheep's clothing...

31
00:05:35,970 --> 00:05:39,710
里面却是残暴的狼
For inwardly, they are ravening wolves.

32
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:43,280
耶稣是保护你们和你们家人
Jesus is the Shepherd who protects you

33
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,850
不受那些狼所害的牧羊人
and your family from those wolves.

34
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:50,520
而我是他的犬
And I am his dog.

35
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:53,650
让迷途羔羊
The sheepdog that gets the lambs back on track

36
00:05:53,660 --> 00:05:55,390
重回正轨的牧羊犬
when they stray off the path.

37
00:05:57,860 --> 00:06:01,430
你们有些人已经走入歧途了 对吗
And some of you have strayed, haven't you?

38
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:06,900
你们是怎么想的
What do you people think?

39
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:09,300
觉得神会同意?
That god is well disposed towards you?

40
00:06:10,670 --> 00:06:13,140
我就直说吧
Let me set things straight.

41
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:16,240
应当离群的那些去的是地狱
Those who deserve it, go to hell.

42
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:19,780
我能跟你们讲讲地狱
I could tell you about hell.

43
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,880
讲讲那里的火焰
About its flames.

44
00:06:23,650 --> 00:06:26,450
讲讲那里的痛苦
About the pain.

45
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:30,020
我肯定你们已经试想过那里的样子
I'm sure you people have tried to imagine what it's like.

46
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:34,360
实则更糟
It's worse.

47
00:06:35,730 --> 00:06:38,300
惩罚要来临了
Retribution is coming.

48
00:06:40,170 --> 00:06:43,900
现在我们唱歌吧
Now, let us join in singing.

49
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,910
与主同行
Abide with me.

50
00:07:08,930 --> 00:07:10,130
你没事吧
You all right?

51
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:17,190
谢谢
Thank you.

52
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:42,660
你好 先生 这是我女儿 珊慕
How're you doing, sir? This is my daughter, Sam.

53
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:46,070
我儿子 马修 还有…
My boy, Matthew. And, uh...

54
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,500
我妻子
My wife.

55
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,070
你去哪了
Where were you?

56
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:04,050
那个人不是本地的
That man is a stranger here,

57
00:08:04,050 --> 00:08:05,820
他还不认识这里的人
he doesn't know anybody yet.

58
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:08,720
我还以为你会有点同情心
I'd have expected a little more compassion from you.

59
00:08:10,230 --> 00:08:12,790
怎么了 怎么了 怎么了
What's wrong? What's wrong? What's wrong?

60
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:32,010
深呼吸 好吗
Just breathe, all right?

61
00:08:32,010 --> 00:08:33,880
呼吸 深呼吸就好
Breathe, just breathe.

62
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:37,850
大家都出去 我们不需要凑热闹的
Everybody outside.We don't need no busybodies.

63
00:08:37,850 --> 00:08:40,090
出去啊 快出去
Go on, get. Get out!

64
00:08:41,690 --> 00:08:46,190
- 会没事的  - 内森 我觉得你最好也出去
- You'll be all right.  - Nathan, I think you better go outside too.

65
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:49,000
有些事是男人不该看的
Some things aren't meant for a man's eyes.

66
00:08:50,830 --> 00:08:53,300
会没事的 对吗 莉兹
It's gonna be just fine, right, Liz?

67
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:57,370
你会照顾好她的 对吧
You're gonna take care of her, right?

68
00:08:57,370 --> 00:08:58,470
保证?
Promise?

69
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:04,350
我要出去了 好吗 我爱你 我爱你
I'm going to be right outside, okay? I love you. I love you.

70
00:09:07,450 --> 00:09:08,950
你照顾好她
You take care of her.

71
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,290
把你身后的门关上
Close the door behind you.

72
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:39,180
会没事的 亲爱的
It's gonna be all right, honey.

73
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:53,630
孩子的头太大了
The baby's head is too big.

74
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:56,030
什么意思
What's that supposed to say?

75
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:58,970
我们得在孩子和母亲之间做出选择
We're going to have to choose between the baby and the mother.

76
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,800
没法同时救两个
Can't save both of them.

77
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,770
必须都救
You have to.

78
00:10:03,810 --> 00:10:06,640
你母亲说一切都会好的
Your mother said everything would be all right.

79
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:16,120
不要 我想待着 我想帮忙
No, I wanna stay. I wanna help.

80
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:29,160
嘿 里面怎么样了
Hey... how's it going in there?

81
00:10:30,570 --> 00:10:31,700
一切都好吗
Everything all right?

82
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:34,050
是吗
Yeah?

83
00:10:56,890 --> 00:11:00,460
用力 阿比 使出全力 加把劲
Push, Abby. Hard as you can now, come on!

84
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:13,310
好样的
Good girl!

85
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:22,320
孩子在哪
Where's the baby?

86
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:25,390
我想看看我的孩子 他在哪
I wanna see my baby. Where is he?

87
00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:28,020
把我的孩子给我
Give me my baby!

88
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:30,750
这不是你的错
It ain't your fault.

89
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:37,520
耶和华赐予了 耶和华又拿走了
The lord gives and the lord takes away.

90
00:12:40,450 --> 00:12:42,790
这和耶和华无关

91
00:12:42,820 --> 00:12:45,500
这和牧师有关

92
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:47,370
牧师？
The reverend?

93
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:50,540
莉兹
Liz...

94
00:12:52,170 --> 00:12:53,710
牧师是神的代表
The reverend is a man of god.

95
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,280
你所认为的并不是事实
You're seeing things that ain't there.

96
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:23,640
耶稣死后复活了
If Jesus came back to life after he was dead...

97
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:27,570
阿比盖尔的孩子不会吗
Couldn't that happen to Abigail's baby, too?

98
00:13:34,350 --> 00:13:35,880
你能给我涂脸吗
Can you face-paint me?

99
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,050
你能帮我一下吗

100
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:24,570
我忙着呢 看不出吗
I'm doing something. Can't you tell?

101
00:14:52,930 --> 00:14:55,200
我们来看下情况
We've come to see if everything's all right.

102
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,660
一切正常
Everything's just fine.

103
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:58,700
你们无需浪费时间
No reason for you folks to go wasting your time.

104
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:03,200
我们想亲眼看下
We'd like to look for ourselves.

105
00:15:03,210 --> 00:15:06,670
最好不要 医生一小时后就到
Rather not. There's a doctor coming in an hour,

106
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:08,380
他看更好
it's better if he takes a look.

107
00:15:11,010 --> 00:15:12,450
牧师安排的
The reverend arranged it.

108
00:15:29,220 --> 00:15:30,430
你们好
Hello!

109
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:10,540
- 什么情况  - 莉兹
- What the hell?  - Liz!

110
00:16:14,810 --> 00:16:16,480
莉兹
Liz!

111
00:16:19,180 --> 00:16:20,810
下来 莉兹
You get down here, Liz!

112
00:16:22,350 --> 00:16:23,750
下来
You get down here!

113
00:16:26,290 --> 00:16:28,460
我要看到你的脸
I wanna see your face.

114
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:34,490
我要看到你的脸
I wanna see your face.

115
00:16:47,710 --> 00:16:51,810
内森 别把气出在我儿子身上
Nathan! Don't take it out on my boy!

116
00:16:51,810 --> 00:16:55,620
我们能好好谈谈
We can talk about this like decent folk!

117
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,920
我跟你没过节 伊莱
I got no quarrel with you, Eli!

118
00:16:59,250 --> 00:17:00,850
我是来找你妻子的
I'm here for your wife.

119
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:04,420
她得为她的罪行受到惩罚
She's gotta be punished for her sins.

120
00:17:05,490 --> 00:17:07,690
她得在火刑柱上被烧死
She's gotta burn at the stake, Eli!

121
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:10,430
理智些 内森
Try to be reasonable now, Nathan.

122
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:13,270
我理解你的悲痛 相信我
I know your sorrow, believe me.

123
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:16,000
我也失去过心爱之人 记得吗
I lost a loved one too, remember?

124
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,370
我知道你的悲痛让你失去了理智
I know you're out of your mind with grief,

125
00:17:18,370 --> 00:17:23,410
但相信我 你的痛苦会过去的 就和我的一样
but believe me, your pain will pass, just like mine did!

126
00:17:23,410 --> 00:17:26,350
我能很容易地接受你说的
I could accept that real easy,

127
00:17:26,350 --> 00:17:30,420
只要那个没舌头的谋杀犯死在火刑柱上
as long as that tongueless murderess ends up at the stake!

128
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:33,690
我要她受到惩罚
I demand retribution!

129
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:38,930
你知道她做了什么吗 伊莱
You know what she did, Eli?

130
00:17:41,600 --> 00:17:43,860
她杀了我的宝贝儿子
She murdered my baby boy.

131
00:17:45,970 --> 00:17:49,000
就在他能受洗之前 她杀了他
Before he could even be baptized, she murdered him.

132
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:56,940
现在他会怎么样
What's gonna happen to him now?

133
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:02,620
你觉得他会找到救赎吗
Do you think he's gonna find salvation?

134
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:09,720
你知道她怎么做的吗 伊莱
You know how she did it, Eli?

135
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:13,930
我看过他
I seen him.

136
00:18:17,370 --> 00:18:19,430
他的大脑外露
His brains had leaked out.

137
00:18:23,840 --> 00:18:25,840
你妻子弄裂了他的头骨
Your wife broke his skull.

138
00:18:28,910 --> 00:18:31,880
她破开了他的头骨
She cracked his skull wide open!

139
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:34,310
她该为此下地狱
She should go to hell for this!

140
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,490
够了
That will be enough.

141
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:41,660
你遭受着痛苦…
There has been suffering...

142
00:18:42,760 --> 00:18:45,390
威士忌让你胡言乱语
It is the whiskey talking now.

143
00:18:45,390 --> 00:18:47,530
当下解决不了问题
This is not the moment to solve this.

144
00:18:50,330 --> 00:18:51,970
她该下地狱 牧师
She belongs in hell, reverend.

145
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,670
他伤到你了吗
Did he do you any harm?

146
00:19:26,700 --> 00:19:29,000
不要让牧师进来

147
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:31,710
他刚刚帮我们脱离了困境
He just helped us out of a real fix.

148
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:07,610
我也能来一杯吗
Do I get one, too?

149
00:20:07,610 --> 00:20:09,840
你还太年轻
You ain't old enough for that yet.

150
00:20:09,850 --> 00:20:11,980
干嘛对这孩子这么苛刻
Why be so hard on the boy?

151
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:14,050
他为了保护家人才有所行动
He only acted to protect his family.

152
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:16,380
他这样做就是成年人了
That makes him an adult.

153
00:20:16,390 --> 00:20:19,390
他母亲不希望他摆弄枪
His mother doesn't want him playing with guns.

154
00:20:19,390 --> 00:20:23,620
年轻人想手持步枪是很自然的事
It's natural for a young man to want to hold a rifle in his hands.

155
00:20:23,630 --> 00:20:26,130
我能把我这杯给马修喝吗
May I offer my glass to Matthew?

156
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:44,340
我想你该去睡觉了 马修
I think it's about time you went back to bed, Matthew.

157
00:20:44,350 --> 00:20:47,280
- 爸爸  - 快 喝了
- Aw, dad!  - Come on, drink up.

158
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:06,200
如果那孩子
None of this would have happened

159
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:08,640
健康完好地被生下 就不会有这种事
if that baby had been born in perfect health.

160
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:13,270
但莉兹对此无能为力
But Liz couldn't do nothing about that.

161
00:21:13,910 --> 00:21:17,240
她决定了谁生谁死
She decided who was to live and who was to die.

162
00:21:17,250 --> 00:21:20,910
那个决定属于神 也只属于神
That decision belongs to god, and god only.

163
00:21:22,180 --> 00:21:24,780
她为什么不把那个选择给留给他呢
Why did she not leave that choice up to him?

164
00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:31,860
也许我该去把她带来
Maybe I should go fetch her.

165
00:22:16,340 --> 00:22:17,740
我知道你在那里
I know you're there,

166
00:22:18,670 --> 00:22:20,210
我也知道你能听到我说话
and I know you can hear me.

167
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:25,050
或许你没舌头
You may have no tongue,

168
00:22:25,050 --> 00:22:27,180
但你的耳朵没问题
but there is nothing wrong with your ears.

169
00:22:31,850 --> 00:22:34,450
你心中为什么会起疑
Why do doubts rise in your heart?

170
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:38,730
你为什么会烦恼
Why are you troubled?

171
00:22:42,330 --> 00:22:44,300
你晚上怎么入睡的
How do you sleep at night?

172
00:22:46,830 --> 00:22:49,770
做谋杀犯是什么感觉
How does it feel to be a murderess?

173
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:03,820
你知道我为什么来这里吗
Do you know why I'm here?

174
00:23:06,350 --> 00:23:07,890
我是来惩罚你的
I'm here to punish you.

175
00:23:11,430 --> 00:23:12,960
你爱这个家吗
Do you love this family?

176
00:23:16,560 --> 00:23:18,160
我见过你女儿了
I've looked at your daughter.

177
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:22,400
她就快是个年轻女人了
She's almost a young woman already.

178
00:23:27,580 --> 00:23:29,040
你在这啊
There you are.

179
00:23:31,250 --> 00:23:32,700
我得走了
I must be going.

180
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:37,750
对内森请不要怀恨在心
Please don't bear a grudge against Nathan in your heart.

181
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:41,220
失去孩子是最难以承受的事
Losing a child is the worst thing a body can go through.

182
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:45,760
我刚跟你妻子也这么说了
I was just talking to your wife about that same thing.

183
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:16,060
你都没感谢他
You didn't even thank him.

184
00:24:18,090 --> 00:24:20,260
实际上 你都没有跟他打招呼
Fact is, you didn't even say hello to him.

185
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:24,770
我们必须离开这里

186
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:28,260
莉兹 内森会恢复理智的
Liz, Nathan will come around.

187
00:24:35,910 --> 00:24:38,850
对了 你知道吗
Right, you know what?

188
00:24:40,450 --> 00:24:42,230
给我一两天时间
Give me a couple of days.

189
00:24:42,750 --> 00:24:44,520
我找人来看管羊
I'll get someone to come in for the sheep...

190
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:48,150
然后我们去我爸那里待一段时间
And then we'll go up to my pa's for a bit.

191
00:24:50,060 --> 00:24:52,090
反正那里就他一个人
He's all alone up there anyway.

192
00:25:58,330 --> 00:25:59,290
爸爸
