I am very disappointed. I had considered many things, but not this.

574
01:10:23,220 --> 01:10:24,560
这就是你想要的吗
Is this what you wanted?

575
01:10:25,460 --> 01:10:26,790
这就是你所追求的吗
What you looked for?

576
01:10:36,300 --> 01:10:38,700
我已准备好原谅你所有的罪
