589
01:11:26,690 --> 01:11:28,620
我不会让你再那么做了
I won't let you do that again.

590
01:11:28,620 --> 01:11:30,050
我会先杀了你
I'll kill you first.

591
01:11:31,990 --> 01:11:34,830
我尝试了 你让我别无选择
I tried. You leave me no choice.

592
01:11:36,530 --> 01:11:39,400
救命 来人啊
Help! Somebody... ah!

593
01:11:39,400 --> 01:11:41,300
来人救命啊
Somebody, help! Ah!

594
01:11:41,300 --> 01:11:43,670
- 你是我的 这是神的旨意  - 救命
- You are mine! It is god's will!  - Help!

595
01:11:43,670 --> 01:11:46,470
救命
Help!

596
01:11:46,470 --> 01:11:48,840
救命 来人啊
Help! Somebody!

597
01:11:52,010 --> 01:11:53,080
出去
Get out!

598
01:11:58,350 --> 01:11:59,680
你个贱人
You whore!

599
01:12:15,000 --> 01:12:17,030
今晚你要跟我走
You're coming with me tonight.

600
01:14:02,610 --> 01:14:03,940
我需要你的帮助
I need your help.

601
01:14:05,980 --> 01:14:08,080
你不会让我惹上麻烦 对吗
You're not gonna get me into trouble, are you?

602
01:14:44,850 --> 01:14:46,320
你确定吗
Are you sure about this?

603
01:14:48,450 --> 01:14:49,850
好了
All right.

604
01:15:01,730 --> 01:15:03,270
我办不到
I can't do this.

605
01:15:45,210 --> 01:15:47,080
你是伊丽莎白·布兰迪吗
Are you Elizabeth brundy?

606
01:16:04,200 --> 01:16:06,060
你确定你要开始这段行程吗
Are you sure you're up to making this trip?

607
01:16:08,020 --> 01:16:09,400
好运
Well, good luck.

608
01:16:11,970 --> 01:16:14,670
别让人看到伤口 依然很新
Don't let anyone see that for a while. It's still pretty fresh.

609
01:17:14,200 --> 01:17:22,300
第三章
起因

610
01:19:48,700 --> 01:19:51,000
我们在天上的父

611
01:19:51,220 --> 01:19:53,200
愿人都尊你的名为圣

612
01:19:53,300 --> 01:19:55,350
愿你的国降临

613
01:20:04,210 --> 01:20:07,850
愿你的旨意行在地上 如同行在天上

614
01:20:08,700 --> 01:20:11,400
我们日用的饮食今日赐给我们

615
01:20:13,580 --> 01:20:15,580
免我们的债
And forgive us our trespasses,

616
01:20:15,580 --> 01:20:18,720
如同我们免了人的债
as we forgive those who trespass against us.

617
01:20:18,720 --> 01:20:20,750
不叫我们遇见试探
And lead us not into temptation,

618
01:20:20,750 --> 01:20:21,890
但救我们脱离凶恶
but deliver us from evil.

619
01:20:22,850 --> 01:20:24,050
因为国度
For thine is the kingdom

620
01:20:24,060 --> 01:20:26,320
权柄 荣耀 全是你的
and the power and the glory,

621
01:20:26,320 --> 01:20:27,960
直到永远 阿门
forever and ever. Amen.

622
01:20:52,320 --> 01:20:53,580
就今晚吧
Tonight.

623
01:20:58,360 --> 01:21:00,190
乔安娜还是在讲荷兰语
Joanna is still speaking Dutch.

624
01:21:00,190 --> 01:21:02,690
我要追究你的责任
I hold you responsible for that.

625
01:21:02,690 --> 01:21:04,630
我会祈求耶和华的帮助
I'll pray for the lord's assistance.

626
01:21:06,500 --> 01:21:08,500
作为妻子 你有你的职责
As a wife, you have your duties.

627
01:21:09,730 --> 01:21:11,870
妻子对自己的身体没有主权
"The wife does not have authority over her own body

628
01:21:11,870 --> 01:21:14,840
丈夫才有 请跟我来吧
"but yields it to her husband." Please come with me.

629
01:21:17,710 --> 01:21:18,840
今晚不行
Not tonight.

630
01:21:22,110 --> 01:21:23,480
你让我别无选择
You leave me no choice.

631
01:21:55,980 --> 01:21:59,020
我们知道我们为什么来这里
We know why we came here.

632
01:21:59,020 --> 01:22:01,520
这里是神的国度
This is god's nation.

633
01:22:01,520 --> 01:22:05,690
耶和华给这个美丽的新国家赐予了他的恩典
The lord shed his grace on this beautiful new country.

634
01:22:06,560 --> 01:22:08,460
这是我们的出埃及记
This was our exodus.

635
01:22:09,390 --> 01:22:10,830
在这座丘陵上的城市
In this city on a hill,

636
01:22:10,830 --> 01:22:14,500
我们将发展一个更纯粹的基督教
we will develop a purer form of christianity.

637
01:22:16,430 --> 01:22:18,200
我们不是都同意
Hadn't we all agreed

638
01:22:18,200 --> 01:22:21,370
抛开旧俗吗
to leave the old language behind?

639
01:22:21,370 --> 01:22:24,810
我们不是都发誓要在这里做得更好吗
Hadn't we sworn to do things better over here?

640
01:22:24,810 --> 01:22:28,440
新世界会把我们从旧世界的罪中解脱
The new world would free us from the sins of the old.

641
01:22:30,380 --> 01:22:33,580
我们是人类的耀眼希望
We are the bright hope of humanity.

642
01:22:34,320 --> 01:22:36,120
这里是应许之地
This is the promised land,

643
01:22:36,120 --> 01:22:40,020
来到这里 我们就都成了神选之人
and by coming here, we have become his chosen people.

644
01:22:42,090 --> 01:22:42,960
阿加莎
Agatha,

645
01:22:43,290 --> 01:22:45,630
你能告诉大家你是怎么领受到召唤的吗
would you tell everyone how you received the calling?

646
01:22:49,800 --> 01:22:52,500
我在家削土豆时
I was at home, peeling potatoes,

647
01:22:52,500 --> 01:22:55,710
出现了巨大白光
when this huge white light appeared.

648
01:22:55,710 --> 01:22:59,010
我看见白光中有个英俊的年轻男子
In that light, i saw a beautiful young man

649
01:22:59,010 --> 01:23:01,180
有着白色翅膀
with white wings.

650
01:23:01,180 --> 01:23:03,880
我问他是不是天使
I asked if he was an angel,

651
01:23:03,880 --> 01:23:07,080
这个年轻男子点点头 露出了微笑
and the young man nodded and smiled.

652
01:23:09,850 --> 01:23:11,450
阿里
Arie,

653
01:23:11,460 --> 01:23:14,390
你能和我们分享一下你目睹的事吗
would you be so kind to share your story of witness with us?

654
01:23:17,290 --> 01:23:21,630
我的差不多一样
For me, it was more or less the same thing,

655
01:23:21,630 --> 01:23:23,370
但出现的不是男的
but it wasn't a man.

656
01:23:23,370 --> 01:23:27,640
在我面前出现的是个美丽的年轻女子
It was a beautiful young woman who showed herself to me.

657
01:23:29,510 --> 01:23:32,980
看见没 我们都是神选之人
You see? We are the chosen people.

658
01:23:32,980 --> 01:23:35,350
显圣这种事并非在任何人身上
A visitation like that is not something that happens

659
01:23:35,350 --> 01:23:37,610
都会发生 你必须争取它
to just anybody. You have to earn it.

660
01:23:41,390 --> 01:23:42,220
安娜
Anna,

661
01:23:43,020 --> 01:23:44,920
你能上前来吗
would you please come to the front?

662
01:24:02,210 --> 01:24:04,440
你怎么说 安娜
What about you, Anna?

663
01:24:04,440 --> 01:24:06,040
你领受到召唤了吗
Have you received the calling yet?

664
01:24:09,650 --> 01:24:11,500
我还没受到这样的祝福
I have not been blessed in such a way.

665
01:24:13,220 --> 01:24:17,420
在我们社区  每个成年人都领受到了召唤 而你却没有
In our community, everyone of age has received such a calling, you have not.

666
01:24:18,560 --> 01:24:22,960
安娜 你做了什么让神如此愤怒
What did you do, Anna, to anger god this much?

667
01:24:27,030 --> 01:24:28,800
我自己的妻子
My own wife,

668
01:24:28,800 --> 01:24:31,170
没法受到神的青睐
who cannot find the lord's favor.

669
01:24:32,500 --> 01:24:33,840
你让我感到耻辱
I am ashamed of you.

670
01:26:29,190 --> 01:26:30,100
天父
Father,

671
01:26:30,100 --> 01:26:33,980
我祈求我妻子对你和对我的爱会增加
I pray that my wife will grow in her love for you,and me.

672
01:26:34,730 --> 01:26:36,830
愿她对我们的爱 注入所有真心
May she love us with all her heart,

673
01:26:36,830 --> 01:26:40,200
所有灵魂 所有思想和所有努力
all her soul, all her mind, and all her might.

674
01:26:40,200 --> 01:26:42,700
赐予我力量 引领她通向
Give me the strength to lead her to the salvation

675
01:26:42,700 --> 01:26:44,530
你恩典下的救赎
provided by your grace.

676
01:26:44,540 --> 01:26:47,200
以耶稣之名 阿门
In Jesus' name, amen.

677
01:28:11,900 --> 01:28:13,550
亲爱的

678
01:28:14,720 --> 01:28:16,300
我要死了

679
01:28:17,750 --> 01:28:20,900
不会的 不会死

680
01:28:22,280 --> 01:28:26,100
这很正常 你这岁数的姑娘都会出现这样的情况

681
01:28:28,550 --> 01:28:29,850
为什么

682
01:28:33,950 --> 01:28:36,580
你现在是女人了 乔安娜

683
01:28:37,750 --> 01:28:40,750
你的身体已做好生孩子的准备

684
01:28:46,920 --> 01:28:48,660
你必须洗洗你女儿
You must wash your daughter.

685
01:28:49,730 --> 01:28:50,990
她不洁净了
She is unclean.

686
01:28:58,370 --> 01:29:00,770
但他从不帮一点忙
But he never raises a finger to help out.

687
01:29:03,970 --> 01:29:05,240
这是女人的命运
It's a woman's fate.

688
01:29:06,180 --> 01:29:07,540
谁说的
Says who?

689
01:29:07,550 --> 01:29:08,840
圣经
Says the Bible.

690
01:29:10,480 --> 01:29:11,810
这不公平
It's not fair.

691
01:29:13,120 --> 01:29:15,520
你父亲是一名教士
Your father's a man of the cloth.

692
01:29:15,520 --> 01:29:18,120
他侍奉神 尘世的家务杂活都留给了他的妻子
He serves god and leaves earthly chores to his wife.

693
01:29:21,490 --> 01:29:22,360
你想干嘛
What do you want?

694
01:29:22,560 --> 01:29:24,430
让我们单独待会儿 我得和这姑娘谈谈
Leave us alone, i have to talk to the girl.

695
01:29:38,140 --> 01:29:40,280
你母亲跟你说了成为女人意味着什么吗
Has your mother told you what it means to be a woman?

696
01:29:42,480 --> 01:29:43,130
说了
Yes.

697
01:29:43,670 --> 01:29:45,680
这血已渗入你的生活
And the blood has penetrated into your life

698
01:29:45,680 --> 01:29:47,170
已驱走你的纯洁
and driven out the innocence.

699
01:29:47,720 --> 01:29:50,750
不用多久 男人们就会开始发现你的魅力
It won't be long before men start to find you attractive.

700
01:29:56,290 --> 01:29:58,560
女人 我知道你在偷听
Woman? I know you're listening.

701
01:29:58,560 --> 01:30:00,760
从现在起 你要把乔安娜当女人来对待
From now on, you must treat Joanna like a woman.

702
01:30:02,170 --> 01:30:04,000
从今天起 猪就由你来管了
As of today, you will do the hogs.

703
01:30:19,480 --> 01:30:20,210
嘿
Hey.

704
01:30:47,880 --> 01:30:49,210
你好 小姐
Hello, lady.

705
01:31:01,860 --> 01:31:03,210
我看到了水泵
I saw the pump.

706
01:31:04,100 --> 01:31:06,230
希望你能
I was hoping you'd be kind enough

707
01:31:06,230 --> 01:31:07,960
让我解渴
to let me quench my thirst.

708
01:31:30,890 --> 01:31:34,320
请允许我表达我最深切的感谢
Allow me to express my deepest thanks.

709
01:31:34,990 --> 01:31:36,280
你们从哪来
Where are you men from?

710
01:31:36,890 --> 01:31:38,530
说来话长
Oh, that's a long story.

711
01:31:39,900 --> 01:31:41,260
以后有机会再说
Maybe some other time.

712
01:31:43,330 --> 01:31:44,470
他怎么办
What about him?

713
01:31:44,470 --> 01:31:46,870
你照顾好他吧
You take care of him.

714
01:31:46,870 --> 01:31:49,140
我猜你是个基督徒
After all, you are a Christian, I assume?

715
01:31:51,440 --> 01:31:52,580
该死的
God damn me.

716
01:32:20,640 --> 01:32:22,440
去马那
Get the horse.

717
01:32:22,440 --> 01:32:24,040
我父母会发现你们两个的
My parents would find you two.

718
01:32:26,000 --> 01:32:29,080
然后把该死的马鞍拿下来
Then get the goddamn saddle.

719
01:32:37,860 --> 01:32:39,190
快走
Go!

720
01:32:40,760 --> 01:32:43,060
快走 离开这里 快
Go on, get out of here! Go on!

721
01:32:54,440 --> 01:32:56,470
得把该死的子弹取出来
Damn bullet needs to get taken out.

722
01:33:01,310 --> 01:33:03,180
然后我也需要照顾
And I need taking care of too.

723
01:33:04,110 --> 01:33:05,880
我父亲会不高兴的
My father won't like that.

724
01:33:05,880 --> 01:33:06,700
是啊…
Yeah...

725
01:33:07,520 --> 01:33:10,120
你知道吗 别他妈告诉他
You know what? Don't fuckin' tell him.

726
01:33:33,580 --> 01:33:34,570
要取了
Here it comes.

727
01:33:58,070 --> 01:34:02,470
我想 是时候自我介绍了
I reckon, it's about time i introduced myself.

728
01:34:05,680 --> 01:34:06,740
我叫塞缪尔
I'm Samuel.

729
01:34:08,980 --> 01:34:10,350
很高兴认识你
It's nice to meet you...

730
01:34:10,750 --> 01:34:11,520
乔安娜
Joanna.

731
01:34:11,890 --> 01:34:13,020
乔安娜
Joanna.

732
01:34:15,490 --> 01:34:16,270
谢谢
Thank you.

733
01:34:31,900 --> 01:34:33,500
这姑娘长得真快
The girl is growing fast.

734
01:34:58,700 --> 01:35:00,060
嗨 亲爱的
Hi, sweetie.

735
01:35:01,130 --> 01:35:02,280
他在发烧
He's running a fever.

736
01:35:02,800 --> 01:35:04,430
你确定吗
Are you sure?

737
01:35:04,440 --> 01:35:06,640
因为据说测体温的最佳方式
'Cause they say the best way to take someone's temperature

738
01:35:06,640 --> 01:35:08,140
是用嘴唇 是吧
is with the lips, huh?

739
01:35:28,390 --> 01:35:29,830
你现在多大了 孩子
How old are you now, child?

740
01:35:31,020 --> 01:35:32,100
十三
Thirteen.

741
01:35:36,470 --> 01:35:39,030
一个完全成年的女人…
A full-grown woman has...

742
01:35:39,040 --> 01:35:42,070
在生活中有着小女孩不能履行的职责
Has duties in life that a young girl can't fulfill.

743
01:35:44,440 --> 01:35:47,340
是我们的主亲自给予的职责
Duties imposed by our lord himself.

744
01:35:53,020 --> 01:35:54,280
请跟我来
Come with me, please.

745
01:36:06,000 --> 01:36:09,030
你母亲总不承担
Your mother does not always assume responsibilities

746
01:36:09,030 --> 01:36:10,430
她应当承担的职责
the way she should.

747
01:36:10,430 --> 01:36:13,400
她不依从她的自然职责
She does not comply with her natural duties.

748
01:36:15,170 --> 01:36:16,610
你明白我的意思吗
Do you understand what I mean?

749
01:36:21,140 --> 01:36:25,580
神让你这么快成为女人 是有原因的
God has made you a woman so soon for a reason.

750
01:36:25,580 --> 01:36:27,150
你或许觉得这是诅咒
You might believe it to be a curse,

751
01:36:27,150 --> 01:36:29,150
但他做的一切都是有原因的
but he has a reason for everything.

752
01:36:30,490 --> 01:36:34,160
你就如使徒保罗笔下所写的那样
You have, as the apostle Paul put it,

753
01:36:34,160 --> 01:36:35,820
过了年岁
"passed the flower of your age."

754
01:36:36,830 --> 01:36:38,130
这可不对
This is not right.

755
01:36:40,300 --> 01:36:41,560
你看到血了
You have seen the blood.

756
01:36:43,230 --> 01:36:44,630
她只是个孩子
She's just a child.

757
01:36:47,370 --> 01:36:50,310
我无需回应你 我只回应神
I need not answer to you. Only to god.

758
01:37:28,180 --> 01:37:29,510
不用了 谢谢 安娜
No, thank you, Anna.

759
01:37:30,450 --> 01:37:31,950
我们的神另有安排
Our god has other plans.

760
01:37:59,810 --> 01:38:01,210
不会有事的
It'll be all right.

761
01:38:03,810 --> 01:38:04,980
双手拿好
Use both hands.

762
