02:10:53,950 --> 02:10:55,220
你喜欢男人吗
Do you like men?

954
02:11:02,960 --> 02:11:04,290
你出过血吗
Have you bled yet?

955
02:11:23,240 --> 02:11:25,450
我是个注定要遭厄运的人 珊慕
I am a doomed man, Sam.

956
02:11:27,850 --> 02:11:29,090
已无法被拯救
Beyond salvation.

957
02:11:29,920 --> 02:11:31,890
我想做什么就做什么
I can do whatever I want.

958
02:11:37,930 --> 02:11:40,930
小女孩仍有着纯洁的气息
Young girls still carry the scent of innocence.

959
02:11:42,460 --> 02:11:45,570
年长的女人闻上去就不同
Older women smell different.

960
02:11:57,140 --> 02:11:58,610
是时候了
The time has come.

961
02:12:46,860 --> 02:12:49,860
人们觉得地狱难以忍受是因为那里的烈焰
People think it's the flames that make hell unbearable.

962
02:12:51,970 --> 02:12:53,030
并不是这样
It's not.

963
02:12:54,340 --> 02:12:56,470
而是因为没有爱
It is the absence of love.

964
02:14:02,340 --> 02:14:03,280
嘿
Hey.

965
02:14:08,310 --> 02:14:09,120
嗯哼
Mmm-hmm.

966
02:14:38,840 --> 02:14:39,650
呀…
Well...

967
02:14:41,110 --> 02:14:42,910
好久不见 莉兹
Long time no see, Liz.

968
02:14:51,120 --> 02:14:52,520
那时我崩溃了
I was a broken man.

969
02:14:53,550 --> 02:14:54,990
无法继续在那生活
Couldn't go on living there.

970
02:14:56,720 --> 02:14:58,130
好在新来的传教士指引了我
Good thing the new preacher showed me

971
02:14:58,130 --> 02:15:00,010
让我去别处试试
I had to go try somewhere else.

972
02:15:00,560 --> 02:15:05,180
是他告诉我毕斯玛司在招副警长
He was the one, told me they was lookin' for deputies up in bismuth.

973
02:15:06,900 --> 02:15:08,870
我在那开启了新的生活
I made myself up a new life there.

974
02:15:11,670 --> 02:15:14,940
大约一年前 那里的警长遭到了枪击
About a year ago, the sheriff there got himself shot.

975
02:15:16,010 --> 02:15:17,710
我被选任代替他的位置
And I was chosen to replace him.

976
02:15:19,610 --> 02:15:21,750
我清理他的办公室时
And while I was cleaning out his office...

977
02:15:25,390 --> 02:15:26,650
发现了这个
I found this.

978
02:15:26,660 --> 02:15:28,910
[通缉令]
[2500美元赏金]
[犯谋杀罪 伊丽莎白·布兰迪 哑巴 没舌头]

979
02:15:31,890 --> 02:15:34,030
你本该改名的 莉兹
You should've changed your name, Liz.

980
02:15:36,130 --> 02:15:37,360
你觉得世界上叫
How many Elizabeth brundys

981
02:15:37,370 --> 02:15:39,130
伊丽莎白·布兰迪的人有多少
you figure there are in this world?

982
02:15:39,130 --> 02:15:42,170
而又有多少是没舌头的
And how many of 'em you figure don't got no tongue?

983
02:15:47,370 --> 02:15:49,180
伊丽莎白·布兰迪
Elizabeth brundy,

984
02:15:49,180 --> 02:15:52,850
你因谋杀你的前雇主兼弗兰克的地狱的业主
I hereby arrest you for the murder of frank blain,

985
02:15:52,850 --> 02:15:56,650
弗兰克·布莱恩 而被捕了
your former employer and proprietor of frank's inferno.

986
02:16:27,720 --> 02:16:29,950
你逃不出你过去的所作所为 莉兹
Your past done caught up with you, Liz.

987
02:17:30,010 --> 02:17:33,710
时光荏苒 影像迷离
As life progresses, images blur.

988
02:17:36,050 --> 02:17:37,880
独留回忆
All that remains are memories.

989
02:17:47,600 --> 02:17:48,700
我清楚地记得她
I remember her well.

990
02:17:51,400 --> 02:17:52,730
她是一名战士
She was a warrior.

991
02:17:53,500 --> 02:17:54,900
始终掌控一切
Always in control.

992
02:18:17,000 --> 02:18:20,330
我常会想她下沉时在想什么
I've often wondered what she was thinking about on her way down.

993
02:18:24,330 --> 02:18:26,300
我会想她想到了我
I like to think she thought of me.

994
02:18:30,170 --> 02:18:33,670
我会想她知道我长大后会变得坚强
I like to think she knew I would grow up to be strong.

995
02:19:28,430 --> 02:19:29,860
我清楚地记得她
I remember her well.

996
02:19:31,000 --> 02:19:32,430
至少我觉得是这样
At least I think I do.

997
02:19:36,340 --> 02:19:39,010
我感觉她一直在我身边
It feels like she always stayed with me.

998
02:19:43,610 --> 02:19:44,880
看守着我
Watching over me.

999
02:19:47,010 --> 02:19:48,550
保护着我
Protecting me.

1000
02:19:48,550 --> 02:19:50,880
嘿 快来 放下那东西
Hey, come on. Put that down.

1001
02:20:06,630 --> 02:20:07,400
妈妈
Mama?

1002
02:20:08,470 --> 02:20:09,740
走吗
You coming?

1003
